flowchart TD
    Req[HTTP request] --> Auth{Valid X-API-Key?}
    Auth -- no --> R401[401 Unauthorized]
    Auth -- yes --> Router[WorldEngineApiRouter]
    Router --> Match{Route matched?}
    Match -- no --> R404[404 Not found]
    Match -- yes --> Ctx["RouteContext<br/>route values, query, body, Services"]
    Ctx --> Ctrl[Controller method]

    Ctrl --> Facade[IWorldEngineFacade]
    Facade --> Sub{Subsystem or CQRS?}
    Sub -- subsystem --> SubCall[ISomeSubsystem.DoAsync]
    Sub -- command --> CDisp[CommandDispatcher]
    Sub -- query --> QDisp[QueryDispatcher]

    CDisp --> CHandler[ICommandHandler]
    CHandler --> Repo[(Repositories)]
    CHandler --> Result[CommandResult]
    Result -->|Success| Bus[IEventBus]
    Bus --> EH[IEventHandler]

    QDisp --> QHandler[IQueryHandler]
    QHandler --> Repo

    SubCall --> Repo

    Result --> Resp[ApiResult]
    QHandler --> Resp
    SubCall --> Resp
    Resp --> JSON["JSON response<br/>camelCase"]
